{"tid":1568442,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[心得]比人打/捉 叫救命技巧","createTime":"2019-09-14T09:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T00:09:30.000Z","uid":60881,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d5ba13eb66d13e256554c2b6721771de10e730b1","tid":1568442,"uid":60881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:45:29.000Z","msg":"呢度教一教大家<br />\n比人打叫幫手 有個技巧既<br />\n唔好淨叫 &ldquo;幫手&rdquo; &ldquo;救命&rdquo;<br />\neg. 應該咁叫&ldquo;帶眼鏡 著牛仔褲 用iphone 高高地 既哥哥 唔好掛住影黎救下我啦&rdquo; <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">要用多啲形容詞</span></span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n原理就係當街上面有1000個自己友 救你既責任就分左比果1000個人，每人分得1/1000 ，所以就冇人想幫手。而當你detailly咁describe左一個人or一小班人既話 要救你既責任感會由1/1000變到 1 or 1/100大好多。 所以有人救你既機會都會變大。 我之前外國心理學堂學返黎希望有用。<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999 有冇巴打明我講咩？ 幫幫手宣傳開佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f3be4a1b557e1670282def8599e1b95661c36e1","tid":1568442,"uid":60881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:45:53.000Z","msg":"自己推 1/10"},{"pid":"94e1f7aae746601537cd327fdbd7ab134971cd1f","tid":1568442,"uid":60881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:46:04.000Z","msg":"自己推 2/10"},{"pid":"a8e7ae893df21e34daa51f3d05d4830c21944071","tid":1568442,"uid":60881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:46:14.000Z","msg":"自己推 3/10"},{"pid":"234989c89dcc619d05921e2effaf4538178ed90a","tid":1568442,"uid":60881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:46:28.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"5613e8f44d87b3f337c97dc3ce50b4608cac9f9d","tid":1568442,"uid":60881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:46:38.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"c6b95bba6f20e5fb828ad0474dbb9413fa9fd6d5","tid":1568442,"uid":60881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:46:48.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"d8b417cbd235ff435098b43861b8bf484eac23ac","tid":156844